      "review_summary": "The PR adds a custom numeric-segment comparator in `src/agents/sessions/model-resolver.ts` and uses it for alias and dated-version candidate sorting.\n\nPR surface: Source +18. Total +18 across 1 file.\n\nReproducibility: yes. as source-reproducible. `parseModelPattern(\"opus\", [claude-opus-4-9, claude-opus-4-10])` reaches current main's plain descending `localeCompare` path and would select the older lexicographic id.",
